<topic template="Default" status="Complete" lasteditedby="robert" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="helpproject.xsd">
  <title>/unsafe</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>/unsafe</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">/unsafe</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">The /unsafe compiler option allows code that uses the unsafe keyword to compile.</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">Syntax</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code with box">/unsafe &#160;</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">Remarks</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">For more information about unsafe code, see Unsafe Code and Pointers.</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3">To set this compiler option in the Visual Studio development environment</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-left:13px; font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-left:13px;">Open the project&apos;s Properties page.</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-left:13px;">Click the Language property page.</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-left:13px;">Set the Allow Unsafe Code property in the General Section</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-left:13px;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">Example</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Compile <text styleclass="Code Example">in.prg</text> for unsafe mode:</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code with box">xsc /unsafe in.prg &#160;</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
  </body>
</topic>
